        <section class="about-section">
            <h2><span class="material-symbols-outlined">precision_manufacturing</span>Our Technology</h2>
            <p>FontVerse leverages cutting-edge machine learning models to analyze thousands of successful font pairings from professional designs. Our system identifies subtle patterns in typography combinations that create visual harmony.</p>
            <p>The algorithm considers multiple factors including x-height ratios, stroke contrast, weight distribution, and historical pairing success rates to recommend combinations that work beautifully together.</p>
            
            <div class="tech-stack">
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h3><span class="material-symbols-outlined">neural</span>Deep Learning</h3>
                    <p>Our custom neural network architecture trained on 50,000+ design samples to understand typographic relationships.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h3><span class="material-symbols-outlined">dataset</span>Design Database</h3>
                    <p>Curated collection of award-winning designs and typography specimens from leading foundries.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h3><span class="material-symbols-outlined">tune</span>Visual Metrics</h3>
                    <p>Proprietary algorithms measuring visual harmony, contrast balance, and readability scores.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="tech-card">
                    <h3><span class="material-symbols-outlined">palette</span>Aesthetic Engine</h3>
                    <p>Style classification system that matches fonts to design moods and brand personalities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        
