        <section class="about-section">
            <h2><span class="material-symbols-outlined">history_edu</span>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>We founded FontVerse to solve a persistent problem in design: even professionals struggle to consistently create harmonious font pairings. Our goal is to augment human creativity with data-driven insights, not replace it.</p>
            <p>The FontVerse algorithm is constantly learning from new design trends and user feedback. Every time you generate or save a pairing, you're helping improve our recommendations for the entire community.</p>
